metadata.name: Candles
metadata.description:
The candle symbolizes hope, faith, persistence, and the continuation of the spirit. Lighting candles is a sign that we are ready to welcome the new year with enthusiasm, persistence, confidence and new hopes for a better future.

Happy New Year!

Photography by Sophan Topati  
Dimensions : 5184 X 3456 Pixels

Taken with Canon EOS 7D and Canon EFS 18-135mm lens.
